  "name": "Morrison COU2 — CPB hemolysis credibility assessment (MRL 5, NC-3 clean package)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under cardiopulmonary bypass (CPB) conditions. COU2 evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class II CPB device at Model Risk Level 5. Full 13-factor assessment: all 13 factors assessed at high rigor with both requiredLevel and achievedLevel populated. Full UQ and sensitivity analysis included. Decision Accepted with thorough rationale grounded in structured evidence.",
