      "rationale": "At MRL 5, software quality assurance requires documented configuration management, version control, regression test suites, and independent code review. The CFD solver (OpenFOAM v9) is under Git version control with tagged releases. A regression test suite of 47 benchmark cases is executed on each release. Independent code review was conducted by a second analyst team. SQA documentation package reviewed and approved by QMS. Achieved Gradation 4: full SQA plan with independent review and automated regression testing.",
